r />\n他又指，警察成為政府的代表默默承受暴徒的指罵、羞辱、襲擊及無窮無盡的報復，慨嘆很多人瞎了眼，看不到暴徒擲磚、同僚血流披面等，只看到聲稱手無寸鐵的學生被警察武力驅趕。<br />\n<br />\n林志偉表示，不論警員對修例立場如何，都會站在前線維持公眾秩序，依法執行職務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔通記你老母係人地指罵你<br />\n唔通坐低都比要比你噴又係襲擊緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nfull gear都講到自己咁委屈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89228108c9436ee3c3cc12a19502bdc95068818e","tid":1234261,"uid":70754,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲公司CS聽電話都代表公司承受指罵羞辱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b197345f68acc82a2f445a5604ee9dbf09034702","tid":1234261,"uid":37730,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:26:22.000Z","msg":"份人工包埋"},{"pid":"5b43ba8fc135cc62f83f7fb0e32684d9dffa0bd4","tid":1234261,"uid":10905,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:26:58.000Z","msg":"講到尾咪又係想加人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你黑警"},{"pid":"31d6f467c49b0fdc37af3dd90f06933d685e6d7c","tid":1234261,"uid":44211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:27:34.000Z","msg":"又割？"},{"pid":"ea6b75ed4631dfec7ec62258c597f4c704a40051","tid":1234261,"uid":4179,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:28:13.000Z","msg":"工係自己選擇 唔好講到咁委屈"},{"pid":"5545e9758ed40c6a0477da6b6b552749943af6e7","tid":1234261,"uid":253981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:29:46.000Z","msg":"做人定做狗自己揀"},{"pid":"ccd682ade7a9914b4936f4155c5573a2d5ee3435","tid":1234261,"uid":20282,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:30:08.000Z","msg":"你代政府打人 咁咪代個政府承受羞辱囉<br />\n好天公地道吖屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143b255417b81adfcada193d61fb935c0edd9b24","tid":1234261,"uid":107405,"like":4,"dislike":0,"s